# mie-postprocessing

Utilities for Mie imaging post-processing (masking, filters, plotting, I/O).

Install locally in editable mode:

```
pip install -e .
```

Then import modules, e.g.:

```
from mie_postprocessing.async_plot_saver import AsyncPlotSaver
```

